===Free Response Sections=== The Free Response sections of the test offer some choice. <ref>https://apstudent.collegeboard.org/apcourse/ap-european-history/about-the-exam</ref> * Short Answer Question (SAQ): (complete 3 of 4) ** Two questions spanning 1600-2001 (''both mandatory'') ** Choice between questions Q3 (periods 1 and 2) and Q4 (periods 3 and 4) * Long Essay Question (LEQ): (complete 1 of 3) ** Choice between questions Q1, (period 1) Q2 (periods 2 and 3) and Q3 (periods 3 and 4)
